28
00:03:43,300 --> 00:03:47,930
【 狮 子 王 】 【The Lion King】

29
00:04:04,420 --> 00:04:07,450
生命真不公平啊！
Life's not fair,is it?

30
00:04:07,630 --> 00:04:11,010
你看我呢，永远都当不上王
You see,I... Well,I shall never be king.

31
00:04:12,630 --> 00:04:17,580
而你永远也见不到明天了
And you shall never see the light of another day.

32
00:04:17,760 --> 00:04:19,550
再见
Adieu.

33
00:04:19,680 --> 00:04:22,390
你妈妈没有教你 不要玩弄你的食物
Didn't your mother tell you not to play with your food?

34
00:04:23,310 --> 00:04:24,350
你想干什么？
What do you want?

35
00:04:24,520 --> 00:04:25,590
我是来这里宣布
I'm here to announce

36
00:04:25,800 --> 00:04:27,880
大王木法沙要来了
that King Mufasa's on his way.

37
00:04:28,020 --> 00:04:30,130
所以对你今天早上 没有出席那个仪式
So you'd better have a good excuse...

38
00:04:30,310 --> 00:04:31,370
最好找个借口
for missing the ceremony this morning.

39
00:04:31,810 --> 00:04:34,420
你害我的午餐都没了
Oh,now,look,Zazu. You've made me lose my lunch.

40
00:04:34,550 --> 00:04:35,990
等大王跟你算帐之后
Ha! You'll lose more than that...

41
00:04:36,150 --> 00:04:37,390
你不见的东西还会更多
when the king gets through with you.

42
00:04:37,560 --> 00:04:39,940
他就像只拉肚子的河马 一样愤怒
He's as mad as a hippo with a hernia.

43
00:04:41,150 --> 00:04:43,440
我怕得全身发抖
Ooh. I quiver with fear!

44
00:04:43,600 --> 00:04:46,350
好了，刀疤，不要那样看我
Now,Scar,don't look at me that way.

45
00:04:46,510 --> 00:04:47,680
救命啊！
Help!

46
00:04:47,850 --> 00:04:50,780
刀疤，吐出来
Drop him.

47
00:04:51,450 --> 00:04:54,290
你来得可真是时候，大王陛下
Impeccable timing,Your Majesty.

48
00:04:57,490 --> 00:05:00,270
这不是我大哥吗？
Why,if it isn't my big brother...

49
00:05:00,430 --> 00:05:03,280
屈尊降贵的 来跟我这普通人厮混
descending from on high to mingle with the commoners.

50
00:05:03,440 --> 00:05:06,350
我跟沙拉碧在辛巴的 介绍仪式中没有看到你
Sarabi and I didn't see you at the presentation of Simba.

51
00:05:06,510 --> 00:05:08,930
那是今天吗？
That was today?

52
00:05:09,360 --> 00:05:11,670
我觉得好害怕呀！
Oh,I feel simply awful!

53
00:05:13,150 --> 00:05:14,810
我八成是给忘了
Must've slipped my mind.

54
00:05:14,980 --> 00:05:17,520
是呀，你忘的不只如此
Yes,well,as slippery as your mind is...

55
00:05:17,720 --> 00:05:21,440
身为大王的弟弟 你应该站在第一位
as the king's brother... you should've been first in line!

56
00:05:22,520 --> 00:05:26,150
我原本是第一位 直到这个小毛球出生
Well,I was first in line... until the little hairball was born.

57
00:05:26,250 --> 00:05:28,760
这个小毛球是我儿子
That hairball is my son...

58
00:05:28,900 --> 00:05:30,760
他也是你未来的国王
and your future king.

59
00:05:31,740 --> 00:05:34,090
我该学学我的礼节啦
Oh,I shall practice my curtsy.

60
00:05:34,260 --> 00:05:36,180
千万不要背对着我，刀疤
Don't turn your back on me,Scar.

61
00:05:36,350 --> 00:05:37,940
不，木法沙
Oh,no,Mufasa.

62
00:05:38,080 --> 00:05:40,330
或许是你不该背对着我
Perhaps you shouldn't turn your back on me.

63
00:05:42,030 --> 00:05:43,530
这是一个挑战吗？
Is that a challenge?

64
00:05:43,700 --> 00:05:45,260
冷静！冷静！
Temper,temper.

65
00:05:45,430 --> 00:05:48,010
我哪敢向大王你挑战呢？
I wouldn't dream of challenging you.

66
00:05:48,440 --> 00:05:50,070
可惜，为什么呢？
Pity. Why not?

67
00:05:50,240 --> 00:05:53,820
要说脑袋的话 我是有狮子的智慧
As far as brains go,I got the lion's share.

68
00:05:54,030 --> 00:05:56,670
说到蛮力嘛…
But when it comes to brute strength...

69
00:05:57,330 --> 00:06:01,640
恐怕我就是基因遗传 比较不明显的例子了
I'm afraid I'm at the shallow end of the gene pool.

70
00:06:04,060 --> 00:06:06,500
每个家庭都会有这个问题 陛下
There's one in every family,sire.

71
00:06:06,670 --> 00:06:08,370
事实上我家有两个
Two in mine,actually...

72
00:06:08,540 --> 00:06:11,280
而且他们总会想尽办法 破坏特别的场合
and they always manage to ruin special occasions.

73
00:06:11,440 --> 00:06:13,370
我该拿他怎么办？
What am I going to do with him?

74
00:06:13,500 --> 00:06:14,910
拿他做地毯会非常好看
He'd make a very handsome throw rug.

75
00:06:15,040 --> 00:06:15,920
沙祖
Zazu!

76
00:06:16,080 --> 00:06:16,960
而且想一想
And just think,

77
00:06:17,160 --> 00:06:20,980
每次弄脏的时候 你可以拿出去打一打
whenever he gets dirty... you could take him out and beat him.

78
00:07:20,070 --> 00:07:21,470
爸，爸
Dad! Dad!

79
00:07:21,640 --> 00:07:24,340
快起来，我们要走了啦！
Come on,Dad,we gotta go! Wake up!

80
00:07:24,510 --> 00:07:25,880
对不起
Sorry.

81
00:07:27,190 --> 00:07:29,210
爸…爸…
Dad. Dad.

82
00:07:29,380 --> 00:07:32,220
你儿子已经醒了
Your son is awake.

83
00:07:32,420 --> 00:07:35,650
在天亮前，他是你儿子
Before sunrise,he's your son.

84
00:07:35,850 --> 00:07:37,930
爸…拜托啦！
Dad! Come on,Dad.

85
00:07:41,800 --> 00:07:43,490
你答应过我的呀！
You promised.

86
00:07:44,640 --> 00:07:45,420
好吧，好吧
- OK,OK.

87
00:07:45,590 --> 00:07:47,970
我醒了，我醒了
I'm up,I'm up.

88
00:08:03,370 --> 00:08:04,250
辛巴，你看
Look,Simba.

89
00:08:05,030 --> 00:08:09,210
阳光所照到的一切 都是我们的国土
Everything the light touches is our kingdom.

90
00:08:10,520 --> 00:08:15,190
一个国王的统治 就跟太阳的起落是相同的
A king's time as ruler rises and falls like the sun.

91
00:08:15,360 --> 00:08:19,470
总有一天，太阳将会 跟我一样慢慢下沉
One day,Simba,the sun will set on my time here...

92
00:08:19,610 --> 00:08:22,540
并且在你当国王的时候 一同上升
and will rise with you as the new king.

93
00:08:22,740 --> 00:08:24,240
这一切都是我的吗？ 所有的一切
- And this'll all be mine? - Everything.

94
00:08:25,420 --> 00:08:28,650
阳光能照到的所有东西…
Everything the light touches.

95
00:08:28,920 --> 00:08:30,750
那有阴影的地方呢？
What about that shadowy place?

96
00:08:30,910 --> 00:08:32,740
那在我们的国度之外
That's beyond our borders.

97
00:08:32,910 --> 00:08:34,010
你绝不可以去那个地方
You must never go there,Simba.

98
00:08:34,180 --> 00:08:36,260
我以为国王可以随心所欲呀！
But I thought a king can do whatever he wants.

99
00:08:36,470 --> 00:08:37,320
你错了
There's more to being king...

100
00:08:37,480 --> 00:08:39,600
国王也不能凡事随心所欲
than getting your way all the time.

101
00:08:39,700 --> 00:08:41,750
不能吗？ 辛巴
- There's more? - Simba...

102
00:08:45,460 --> 00:08:48,230
世界上所有的生命 都有他存在的价值
Everything you see exists together... in a delicate balance.

103
00:08:48,400 --> 00:08:52,510
身为国王，你不但要了解
As king,you need to understand that balance...

104
00:08:52,640 --> 00:08:54,400
还要去尊重所有的生活
and respect all the creatures...

105
00:08:54,540 --> 00:08:57,350
包括爬行的蚂蚁和跳跃的羚羊
from the crawling ant to the leaping antelope.

106
00:08:57,480 --> 00:08:59,240
但是，爸… 我们不是吃羚羊吗？
But,Dad,don't we eat the antelope?

107
00:08:59,380 --> 00:09:02,080
是呀，我来跟你解释一下
Yes,Simba,but let me explain.

108
00:09:02,220 --> 00:09:04,960
我们死后呢，尸体会成为草
When we die,our bodies become the grass...

109
00:09:05,100 --> 00:09:07,740
而羚羊是吃草的
and the antelope eat the grass.

110
00:09:07,910 --> 00:09:08,790
所以…
And so

111
00:09:08,950 --> 00:09:10,900
在这个生命圈里面
we are all connected

112
00:09:11,040 --> 00:09:12,800
都是互相有关联的
in the great circle of life.

113
00:09:13,000 --> 00:09:14,110
早安，陛下
- Good morning,sire!

114
00:09:14,250 --> 00:09:15,120
沙祖，你早
- Good morning,Zazu.

115
00:09:15,290 --> 00:09:17,080
我来做早上的例行报告
Checking in with the morning report. Fire away.

116
00:09:17,220 --> 00:09:17,860
你说吧 黑猩猩激动 而长颈鹿高高在上
Chimps are going ape,giraffes remain above it all

117
00:09:21,240 --> 00:09:24,010
大象非常清楚我所忘记的事情
Elephants remember,though just what,I can't recall

118
00:09:24,180 --> 00:09:26,850
鳄鱼爬到岸上咬住新鲜的猎物
Crocodiles are snapping up fresh offers from the banks

119
00:09:27,060 --> 00:09:28,580
他向我展示巢里的蛋
Shown interest in my nest egg,

120
00:09:28,720 --> 00:09:30,160
我说不客气
but I quickly said,no,thanks

121
00:09:30,320 --> 00:09:33,160
我们没去看犀鸟 而秃鹰有第六感
We haven't paid the hornbills,and the vultures have a hunch

122
00:09:33,330 --> 00:09:37,410
不是每个受邀的人 都会来吃午餐
Not everyone invited will be coming back from lunch

123
00:09:37,580 --> 00:09:42,110
哈哈，这就是晨间报告
This is the morning report

124
00:09:42,280 --> 00:09:44,500
大事小事不漏掉
Gives you the long and the short

125
00:09:45,290 --> 00:09:48,490
每个呼吸微笑
Every grunt,roar,and snort

126
00:09:48,620 --> 00:09:51,360
每个轻声吼叫
Not a tale I distort

127
00:09:51,530 --> 00:09:55,710
都在晨间报告
On the morning report

128
00:09:55,910 --> 00:09:57,180
儿子，你在干什么？  扑东西
- What are you doing,son? - Pouncing.

129
00:09:57,310 --> 00:09:58,060
让个老手示范给你看看
Let an old pro show you how it's done.

130
00:10:00,780 --> 00:10:01,660
今年草地肥美
Oh,the buffalo

131
00:10:01,860 --> 00:10:04,630
水牛个个吃得强又壮 尽量的压低身子
have got a beef about...

132
00:10:04,770 --> 00:10:06,430
豪猪受到阻挠 趴在地上
Stay low to the ground.

133
00:10:06,600 --> 00:10:08,260
意图节省他毒气 趴在地上，好，我知道了
Yeah,OK. Stay low to the ground. Right.

134
00:10:08,460 --> 00:10:11,070
…不停追逐文书鸟 别出声
Not a sound.

135
00:10:11,200 --> 00:10:13,250
番红花是本季色彩 随处都可见
The season's colors seen in all the herds...

136
00:10:13,460 --> 00:10:17,670
动一动行列纵队进行慢慢往下 慢慢来，向前一步
Take it slow. One more step...

137
00:10:17,800 --> 00:10:19,950
…聚集在水肥处 然后…
- then... ...in the dung

138
00:10:22,150 --> 00:10:24,860
这就是晨间报告
This is the morning report

139
00:10:24,990 --> 00:10:27,920
大事小事不漏掉
Gives you the long and the short

140
00:10:28,130 --> 00:10:30,970
