Every grunt,roar,and snort

141
00:10:31,140 --> 00:10:33,980
每个轻声吼叫
Not a tale I distort

142
00:10:34,110 --> 00:10:38,710
都在晨间报告
On the morning report

143
00:10:44,610 --> 00:10:45,480
哈…非常好 Ha …It is very good

144
00:10:46,490 --> 00:10:47,810
沙祖 什么事呀？
- Zazu! - Yes!

145
00:10:47,940 --> 00:10:49,230
地下传来的消息
Sir! News from the underground.

146
00:10:49,390 --> 00:10:50,580
好，这一次呢…  陛下
Now,this time... Sire!

147
00:10:50,680 --> 00:10:51,350
土狼到了荣耀石啦！
Hyenas in the pride lands!

148
00:10:54,130 --> 00:10:55,840
沙祖，带辛巴回家
Zazu,take Simba home.

149
00:10:56,010 --> 00:10:56,840
我不能去吗？
- Dad,can't I come?

150
00:10:57,010 --> 00:10:58,810
不行，儿子
- No,son.

151
00:10:59,330 --> 00:11:01,260
哼！什么地方都不准我去
I never get to go anywhere.

152
00:11:01,430 --> 00:11:05,170
哦，小主人 将来你也会当国王的
Oh,young master,one day,you will be king.

153
00:11:05,370 --> 00:11:08,590
然后你就可以随心所欲地 去追逐那些流着口水
Then you can chase those slobbering,mangy...

154
00:11:08,760 --> 00:11:11,820
卑贱愚蠢的非法入侵者
stupid poachers from dawn until dusk.

155
00:11:15,300 --> 00:11:17,940
嘿！刀疤叔叔，你猜怎样？
Hey,Uncle Scar! Guess what?

156
00:11:18,110 --> 00:11:20,790
我最痛恨猜谜游戏了
I despise guessing games.

157
00:11:20,950 --> 00:11:22,980
我将成为这里的国王耶
I'm gonna be king of Pride Rock.

158
00:11:23,120 --> 00:11:24,920
哦！真好啊
Oh,goody.

159
00:11:25,060 --> 00:11:27,310
我爸刚刚带我看了整个国度
My dad just showed me the whole kingdom...

160
00:11:27,510 --> 00:11:29,770
而我将会统治一切
and I'm gonna rule it all.

161
00:11:29,900 --> 00:11:31,220
是啊
Yes,well

162
00:11:31,390 --> 00:11:33,380
哦！请原谅我没有高兴地跳起来
forgive me for not leaping for joy.

163
00:11:33,520 --> 00:11:36,710
我的背不好你知道的
Bad back,you know.

164
00:11:36,850 --> 00:11:37,870
嘿，刀疤叔叔
Hey,Uncle Scar,

165
00:11:38,010 --> 00:11:40,100
如果我是国王 那你是什么？
when I'm king,what'll that make you?

166
00:11:40,300 --> 00:11:42,330
你这猴子
A monkey's uncle.

167
00:11:42,500 --> 00:11:44,110
你好奇怪哦！
You're so weird.

168
00:11:44,280 --> 00:11:46,270
还有更怪的呢！
You have no idea.

169
00:11:46,440 --> 00:11:49,470
哦！原来你爸爸带你 看过整个王国了，是吗？
So,your father showed you the whole kingdom,did he?

170
00:11:49,610 --> 00:11:50,570
看过啦
Everything.

171
00:11:50,770 --> 00:11:53,770
他没有带你到北方边界 太阳升起的地方吗？
He didn't show you what's beyond that rise... at the northern border?

172
00:11:53,910 --> 00:11:55,830
没有
Well,no.

173
00:11:55,970 --> 00:11:57,230
他说我不能去那里
He said I can't go there.

174
00:11:57,360 --> 00:11:59,290
他说的完全正确
And he's absolutely right.

175
00:11:59,490 --> 00:12:00,490
那里太危险了
It's far too dangerous.

176
00:12:00,660 --> 00:12:03,070
只有勇敢的狮子才会去呀
Only the bravest lions go there.

177
00:12:03,180 --> 00:12:04,850
我很勇敢啊  那有什么？
Well,I'm brave. What's out there?

178
00:12:05,020 --> 00:12:05,690
对不起，辛巴 我就是不能告诉你
I'm sorry,Simba,I just can't tell you.

179
00:12:08,250 --> 00:12:08,890
为什么？
Why not?

180
00:12:09,030 --> 00:12:10,670
辛巴，辛巴
Simba,Simba,

181
00:12:10,870 --> 00:12:13,610
我只是在为我 最喜欢的侄子着想
I'm only looking out... for the well-being of my favorite nephew.

182
00:12:13,740 --> 00:12:16,450
没错，我是你唯一的侄子
Yeah,right. I'm your only nephew.

183
00:12:16,590 --> 00:12:18,940
所以罗，我才更要保护你
All the more reason for me to be protective.

