I finally got some sense knocked into me...

1138
01:08:44,050 --> 01:08:46,310
我头上还有包包可以证明呢！
and I've got the bump to prove it.

1139
01:08:46,470 --> 01:08:48,890
话说回来这是我的国度
Besides,this is my kingdom.

1140
01:08:49,030 --> 01:08:51,770
如果我不为它而战 还有谁会？
If I don't fight for it,who will?

1141
01:08:51,930 --> 01:08:53,220
我会
- I will.

1142
01:08:53,390 --> 01:08:54,740
这是很危险的
- It's gonna be dangerous.

1143
01:08:54,870 --> 01:08:55,960
危险？哼！
Danger? Ha!

1144
01:08:56,160 --> 01:08:58,840
我会当面嘲笑危险 哈哈…
I laugh in the face of danger.

1145
01:08:59,300 --> 01:09:00,970
我觉得这件事一点也不好笑
I see nothing funny about this.

1146
01:09:01,140 --> 01:09:03,940
丁满、彭彭 你们来这儿干嘛？
Timon,Pumbaa,what are you doing here?

1147
01:09:04,110 --> 01:09:06,170
我们随时为陛下服务
At your service,my liege.

1148
01:09:06,270 --> 01:09:08,040
哦，我们就为了这些…
Oh,we're gonna

1149
01:09:08,210 --> 01:09:10,050
要向你叔叔挑战？
fight your uncle for this?

1150
01:09:10,240 --> 01:09:13,050
是的，丁满 这里是我的家
Yes,Timon. This is my home.

1151
01:09:13,180 --> 01:09:15,830
哦，这里是该大肆整顿了
Oh,talk about your fixer-upper.

1152
01:09:16,020 --> 01:09:17,150
哦，辛巴
Well,Simba,

1153
01:09:17,280 --> 01:09:21,700
如果这对你很重要 我们会永远支持你
if it's important to you... we're with you to the end.

1154
01:09:37,090 --> 01:09:40,500
土狼…我恨土狼
Hyenas. I hate hyenas.

1155
01:09:40,670 --> 01:09:43,280
要穿过那些家伙 你有什么好计划？
So,what's your plan for getting past those guys?

1156
01:09:43,480 --> 01:09:44,440
用活的饵
- Live bait.

1157
01:09:44,610 --> 01:09:46,700
好主意
- Good idea. Hey!

1158
01:09:46,870 --> 01:09:49,410
来吧，丁满 你们去分散他们的注意力
Come on,Timon. You guys have to create a diversion.

1159
01:09:49,580 --> 01:09:52,650
你要我怎么做？ 穿上裙子跳草裙舞吗？
What do you want me to do,dress in drag and do the hula?

1160
01:09:53,620 --> 01:09:55,330
假如你要尝尝美味多汁的鲜肉
If you're hungry for a hunk of fat and juicy meat

1161
01:09:55,460 --> 01:09:57,230
远在天边近在眼前不必花心思
Eat my buddy Pumbaa here because he is a treat

1162
01:09:57,400 --> 01:09:59,330
这只猪很肥包你吃满意
Come on down and dine on this tasty swine

1163
01:09:59,500 --> 01:10:00,820
不必客气快来吃个饱
All you have to do is get in line

1164
01:10:01,310 --> 01:10:03,270
你会痛吗？ 砰砰砰
- Are you achin' - Yep,yep,yep.

1165
01:10:03,440 --> 01:10:05,010
来，先来一客 砰砰砰
- For some bacon? - Yep,yep,yep.

1166
01:10:05,120 --> 01:10:06,440
瞧瞧他有多棒 砰砰
- He's a big pig - Yep yep.

1167
01:10:06,600 --> 01:10:09,700
你可以向他一样酷
You could be a big pig,too,oy!

1168
01:10:13,510 --> 01:10:14,320
娜娜
Nala,

1169
01:10:14,450 --> 01:10:16,810
你先去找我妈 然后集合所有的狮子
you find my mother and rally the lionesses.

1170
01:10:16,970 --> 01:10:19,160
我去找刀疤
I'll look for Scar.

1171
01:10:22,270 --> 01:10:25,330
沙拉碧
Sarabi!

1172
01:10:38,060 --> 01:10:39,250
什么事？刀疤
Yes,Scar?

1173
01:10:39,450 --> 01:10:41,250
你们的狩猎队呢？
Where is your hunting party?

1174
01:10:41,420 --> 01:10:42,770
他们没有尽职地工作
They're not doing their job.

1175
01:10:42,900 --> 01:10:44,580
刀疤，已经没有食物了
Scar,there is no food.

1176
01:10:44,750 --> 01:10:45,610
动物都离开了
The herds have moved on.

1177
01:10:45,780 --> 01:10:48,170
不！他们只是没有认真找而已
No,you're just not looking hard enough.

1178
01:10:48,330 --> 01:10:52,110
结束了，这里什么都没有
It's over. There is nothing left.

1179
01:10:52,300 --> 01:10:54,300
我们只剩下一个选择
We have only once choice.

1180
01:10:54,470 --> 01:10:56,010
我们必须离开荣耀石
We must leave Pride Rock.

1181
01:10:56,110 --> 01:10:57,470
我们什么地方都不去
We're not going anywhere.

1182
01:10:57,600 --> 01:10:59,400
那么你是在判我们死刑
Then you have sentenced us to death.

1183
01:10:59,540 --> 01:11:00,270
那么就死吧
- Then so be it.

1184
01:11:00,470 --> 01:11:01,600
你不能那么做
- You can't do that.

1185
01:11:01,700 --> 01:11:04,060
我是国王我爱怎么做都可以
I am the king. I can do whatever I want.

1186
01:11:04,220 --> 01:11:06,280
如果你有木法沙王的一半…
If you were half the King Mufasa was...

1187
01:11:06,450 --> 01:11:09,190
我比木法沙王要强上十倍
I'm ten times the king Mufasa was!

1188
01:11:11,490 --> 01:11:12,420
木法沙？
Mufasa?

1189
01:11:12,680 --> 01:11:15,090
不！你死了
No,you're dead.

1190
01:11:21,140 --> 01:11:22,850
木法沙？
Mufasa?

1191
01:11:24,050 --> 01:11:26,590
不，是我
No. It's me.

1192
01:11:26,760 --> 01:11:27,980
辛巴？
Simba.

1193
01:11:28,120 --> 01:11:29,960
你还活着？
You're alive?

1194
01:11:30,150 --> 01:11:31,540
怎么可能呢？
How can that be?

1195
01:11:31,670 --> 01:11:33,150
这不重要
It doesn't matter.

1196
01:11:33,350 --> 01:11:35,380
我回来了
I'm home.

1197
01:11:35,480 --> 01:11:36,670
辛巴？
Simba?

1198
01:11:36,810 --> 01:11:38,930
辛巴！
Simba!

1199
01:11:39,130 --> 01:11:43,840
看到你还活着 真让我有一点…惊讶
Oh,I'm a little surprised to see you... alive.

1200
01:11:44,820 --> 01:11:47,460
给我一个好理由 让我不致于撕烂你
Give me one good reason why I shouldn't rip you apart.

1201
01:11:47,590 --> 01:11:49,620
辛巴，你一定要了解
Oh,Simba,you must understand.

1202
01:11:49,820 --> 01:11:52,140
统治一个国度的压力呀！
The pressures of ruling a kingdom...

1203
01:11:52,280 --> 01:11:55,300
这国度不再是你的了 退位吧，刀疤
Are no longer yours. Step down,Scar.

1204
01:11:55,410 --> 01:11:57,250
哈…是啊 我会的
Oh,well,I would,

1205
01:11:57,410 --> 01:11:58,530
当然会啦！
naturally.

1206
01:11:58,740 --> 01:12:00,990
但是这里有个小问题
However,there is one little problem.

1207
01:12:01,120 --> 01:12:02,960
看到他们没有？
You see them?

1208
01:12:04,130 --> 01:12:06,610
他们认为我是国王
They think I'm king.

1209
01:12:06,780 --> 01:12:07,870
我们不认为
Well,we don't.

1210
01:12:08,000 --> 01:12:10,130
辛巴才是合法的国王
Simba's the rightful king.

1211
01:12:10,330 --> 01:12:12,170
选择权在你手上
The choice is yours,Scar.

1212
01:12:12,330 --> 01:12:14,420
退位不然就战斗
Either step down or fight.

1213
01:12:14,560 --> 01:12:17,270
难道非要用暴力解决吗？
Oh,must this all end in violence?

1214
01:12:17,430 --> 01:12:21,150
我不喜欢为 家族成员的死亡来负责
I'd hate to be responsible... for the death of a family member.

1215
01:12:21,310 --> 01:12:22,630
你同意吗？辛巴
Wouldn't you agree,Simba?

1216
01:12:22,800 --> 01:12:24,570
你说这些都没有用，刀疤
That's not gonna work,Scar.

1217
01:12:24,730 --> 01:12:25,890
我已经把它遗忘了
I've put it behind me.

1218
01:12:26,030 --> 01:12:27,800
但是你那些忠实的臣民呢？
But what about your faithful subjects?

1219
01:12:27,960 --> 01:12:29,700
他们也忘掉了吗？
Have they put it behind them?

1220
01:12:29,840 --> 01:12:31,800
辛巴，他到底在说什么？
Simba,what is he talking about?

1221
01:12:31,940 --> 01:12:36,100
哦！你还没有告诉她们 你那些小秘密？
Ah,so you haven't told them your little secret.

1222
01:12:36,260 --> 01:12:39,190
辛巴，现在你有机会告诉他们
Well,Simba,now's your chance to tell them.

1223
01:12:39,330 --> 01:12:44,130
告诉他们木法沙的死 到底该由谁来负责！
Tell them who is responsible for Mufasa's death.

1224
01:12:46,690 --> 01:12:48,600
是我
I am.

1225
01:12:51,930 --> 01:12:54,370
这不是真的
It's not true.

1226
01:12:54,510 --> 01:12:57,860
告诉我这不是真的
Tell me it's not true.

1227
01:12:58,350 --> 01:12:59,440
是真的
- It's true.

1228
01:12:59,640 --> 01:13:01,600
看吧，他承认了
- You see? He admits it!

1229
01:13:01,740 --> 01:13:02,970
凶手…
Murderer!

1230
01:13:03,100 --> 01:13:04,390
不！那只是个意外
No,it was an accident.

1231
01:13:04,520 --> 01:13:06,260
如果不是为了你 木法沙还会活着
If it weren't for you,Mufasa would still be alive.

1232
01:13:06,430 --> 01:13:08,900
他的死是你的错 你能否认吗？
It's your fault he's dead! Do you deny it?

1233
01:13:09,040 --> 01:13:09,710
不能
No

1234
01:13:09,850 --> 01:13:12,110
那么你是有罪的了
Then you're guilty.

1235
01:13:12,240 --> 01:13:13,400
不！我不是凶手
No,I'm not a murderer.

1236
01:13:13,630 --> 01:13:16,110
辛巴，你又再度有麻烦了
Oh,Simba,you're in trouble again...

1237
01:13:16,250 --> 01:13:19,050
但是这一回爸爸 可没办法来救你了
but this time,daddy isn't here to save you...

1238
01:13:19,220 --> 01:13:22,700
现在每个人都知道原因了
and now everyone knows why!

1239
01:13:22,960 --> 01:13:24,870
辛巴
Simba

1240
01:13:30,360 --> 01:13:34,140
这一幕看起来很眼熟
Now,this looks familiar.

1241
01:13:34,360 --> 01:13:37,660
我以前在哪儿看过？ 我想想看哦！
Where have I seen this before?

1242
01:13:38,210 --> 01:13:41,100
哦！对了！我想到了
Let me think.

1243
01:13:41,270 --> 01:13:45,200
这正是你爸爸 要死之前的那个情景
Oh,yes. I remember. This is just the way your father looked before he died.

1244
01:13:46,830 --> 01:13:50,790
而这是我的小秘密
And here's my little secret...

1245
01:13:51,000 --> 01:13:54,610
我杀了木法沙
I killed Mufasa.

1246
01:13:57,100 --> 01:13:59,060
凶手
Murderer!

1247
01:13:59,200 --> 01:14:00,350
不！辛巴，求求你
No,Simba,please.

1248
01:14:00,520 --> 01:14:01,550
告诉他们真相
Tell them the truth.

1249
01:14:01,690 --> 01:14:02,520
真…相？
Truth?

1250
01:14:02,690 --> 01:14:05,130
但是每个人对真相的看法都…
But truth is in the eye of the behold...

1251
01:14:06,270 --> 01:14:11,340
好…是我干的
All right. All right. I did it.

1252
01:14:11,440 --> 01:14:14,050
让大家都听得见
So they can hear you.

1253
01:14:14,220 --> 01:14:18,150
我杀了木法沙
I killed Mufasa!

1254
01:14:29,590 --> 01:14:33,070
我打、我踢、我踹 我砍、我砍、我咬
Excuse me. Pardon me. Comin' through. Hot stuff.

1255
01:15:00,720 --> 01:15:01,880
放我出去，放我出去
- Let me out! Let me out!

1256
01:15:01,980 --> 01:15:03,400
让我进去，让我进去
- Let me in! Let me in!

1257
01:15:05,110 --> 01:15:06,620
拜托不要吃我
Please,don't eat me.

1258
01:15:06,790 --> 01:15:08,210
放下他们
Drop 'em!

1259
01:15:08,730 --> 01:15:09,720
那只猪是谁呀？
- Hey,who's the pig?

1260
01:15:09,860 --> 01:15:10,530
你是在叫我吗？
- Are you talkin' to me?

1261
01:15:10,670 --> 01:15:11,630
他在叫他猪
- Uh-oh,they called him a pig.

1262
01:15:11,770 --> 01:15:13,190
你在叫我吗？ 怎么可以叫他猪
- Shouldn't have done that. - Are you talking to me?

1263
01:15:13,290 --> 01:15:15,310
你在叫我吗？ 你们糗大罗
- Now they're in for it.Take that,you stupid...

1264
01:15:15,450 --> 01:15:20,970
他们都管我叫猪大爷
- They call me Mister Pig!

1265
01:15:53,690 --> 01:15:54,710
凶手
Murderer.

1266
01:15:54,820 --> 01:15:55,770
辛巴，辛巴
Simba. Simba,please.

1267
01:15:55,950 --> 01:15:57,910
求求你 求求你大发慈悲
Please,have mercy. I beg you.

1268
01:15:58,430 --> 01:16:00,140
你根本不配活着
You don't deserve to live.

1269
01:16:00,270 --> 01:16:01,720
但…是，辛巴…
But,Simba,

1270
01:16:01,890 --> 01:16:05,750
我是…我是你的家人
I am family.

1271
01:16:05,930 --> 01:16:08,670
那些土狼才是我们真正的敌人
It's the hyenas who are the real enemy.

1272
01:16:08,800 --> 01:16:11,340
都是他们的错 是他们的点子
It was their fault. It was their idea.

1273
01:16:11,510 --> 01:16:13,840
我为什么要相信你？
Why should I believe you?

1274
01:16:14,000 --> 01:16:16,640
你告诉我的每一件事都是谎言
Everything you ever told me was a lie.

1275
01:16:16,740 --> 01:16:18,390
你打算要怎么做呢？
What are you going to do?

1276
01:16:18,580 --> 01:16:22,100
你该不会杀了你的亲叔叔吧？
You wouldn't kill your own uncle.

1277
01:16:22,200 --> 01:16:24,810
不，刀疤
No,Scar,

1278
01:16:24,980 --> 01:16:27,070
我可不像你
I'm not like you.

1279
01:16:27,240 --> 01:16:29,530
辛巴，谢谢你 太好了
Oh,Simba,thank you. You are truly noble.

1280
01:16:29,730 --> 01:16:31,110
我保证会补偿你的
I'll make it up to you,I promise.

1281
01:16:31,240 --> 01:16:33,300
我该怎么做才能向你证明呢？
And how can I prove myself to you?

1282
01:16:33,510 --> 01:16:35,500
告诉我什么都行
Tell me. I mean,anything.

1283
01:16:35,670 --> 01:16:36,630
好
Run.

1284
01:16:37,320 --> 01:16:39,120
离开这里，刀疤
Run away,Scar,

1285
01:16:39,250 --> 01:16:42,350
永远不要再回来
and never return.

1286
01:16:42,520 --> 01:16:46,290
是啊，当然啦
Yes. Of course.

1287
01:16:47,070 --> 01:16:48,880
如你所愿
As you wish,your

1288
01:16:49,040 --> 01:16:51,330
国王陛下
majesty!

1289
01:17:43,650 --> 01:17:45,910
我的朋友们
My friends.

1290
01:17:46,070 --> 01:17:47,400
朋友们？
Friends?

1291
01:17:47,530 --> 01:17:49,690
我好像听他说 我们是他的敌人
I thought he said we were the enemy.

1292
01:17:49,890 --> 01:17:52,430
是啊！我也是这么听说的
Yeah. That's what I heard.

1293
01:17:52,530 --> 01:17:55,110
阿德？
- Ed? - Ed?

1294
01:17:57,960 --> 01:18:00,400
不，听着，我可以解释
No,no. Let me explain.

1295
01:18:00,570 --> 01:18:01,830
你们并不了解
No,you don't understand!

1296
01:18:02,000 --> 01:18:03,540
不…我不是故意的
No,I didn't mean...

1297
01:18:03,710 --> 01:18:07,060
不…听我解释
No..

1298
01:19:09,070 --> 01:19:11,330
是时候了
It is time.

1299
01:19:34,880 --> 01:19:37,690
要记住
Remember.

1300
01:20:18,250 --> 01:20:22,960
靠着阳光走
Till we find our place

1301
01:20:23,160 --> 01:20:28,450
慢慢你会知道
On the path unwinding

1302
01:20:29,040 --> 01:20:38,010
看这世界生生不息
In the circle

1303
01:20:38,630 --> 01:20:42,600
生生不息
The circle of life

